      <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-87e432f7ed704b3aa7835782327baf42" textAlignment="1">
        <bounds x="528" y="799" width="434" height="108"/>
        <content>The Unicorn project is designed to streamline the documentation and sharing of architecture artifacts created on a Kindle Scribe. Its primary objective is to enable users to export diagrams and Architecture Decision Records (ADRs) from Kindle Scribe, convert them into Markdown format, and host them on a secure, static website for easy access and collaboration.</content>
        <property key="URL" value="https://hugo.royerm.fr/adr/0002-architecture-decision-repository/"/>
      </child>
